short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension that improves your bookmarks efficiency.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Super Bookmarks is a bookmark browser extension. It allows you to open your bookmarks conveniently and quickly. You only need to press the shortcut key (Ctrl+B on Windows, Command+E on Mac) to quickly open this extension and open bookmarks. At the same time, Super Bookmarks also supports search function, which can quickly find the bookmarks you need to open.
